            . On the 18th of May I was riding through <placeName id="t18190526-72-crimeloc397">Islington</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18190526-72-crimeloc397" type="placeName" value="Islington"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18190526-72-crimeloc397" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190526-72-off395 t18190526-72-crimeloc397"></join> in my chaise, and missed my coat off the chaise; I turned round, and saw the prisoner with it - I called Stop thief! and he was taken with it. It could not have fallen out.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18190526-72-person696">
                  JAMES 
                  SMITH
               <interp inst="t18190526-72-person696" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
